verbose_text: While the US-made product, despite a slight increasing trend, did not affect significantly the values of TEER compared to control at all time intervals, the Italy-made VSL # 3 induced a time dependent TEER reduction when compared to both untreated and US-made probiotic treated cells which was statistically significant at 3 and 6 h incubation (P < 0.01 at 3 h and P < 0.001 at 6 h vs untreated; P < 0.001 at 3 h and P < 0.0001 at 6 h vs US-made VSL # 3).
